ItemDesc: Upon use, immediately heals one ally by <unbreak>15%</unbreak> of the ally's Max HP plus <unbreak>150</unbreak> extra HP.
ItemBGDesc: Berrypheasants live in symbiosis with plants, with a lot of fruit hanging from their tails. Berrypheasant Skewers are actually fruit skewers, and no Berrypheasants were harmed during the production process. "So... is this a meat dish or a vegetarian dish?"
